text: Knut Börje Stattin (13 February 1930 - 4 April 2020) was a Swedish gymnast. He competed in all gymnastics events at the 1952 Summer Olympics with the best individual result of 37th place on horizontal bar. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Swedish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Gävle
